Uses of Package
elements

  • Packages that use elements 
    Package Description
    controller
    Contains the PetriNet and its implemented interface.
    elements
    Contains all of the classes to add inside a PetriNet.
  • Classes in elements used by controller 
    Class Description
    Edge
    A base element which links one Transition and one Place.
    EmptyingEdge
    An InputEdge which clears all of the tokens inside its Place if it has any.
    InputEdge
    An Edge meant to be linked from a Place to a Transition and remove tokens from the Place if it has enough.
    OutputEdge
    An Edge meant to be linked from a Transition to a Place and add tokens to it.
    Place
    A base element which stores tokens.
    Transition
    A base element which can be triggered to make a step.
    ZeroEdge
    An InputEdge which can be triggered only if its Place is empty.
  • Classes in elements used by elements 
    Class Description
    Edge
    A base element which links one Transition and one Place.
    InputEdge
    An Edge meant to be linked from a Place to a Transition and remove tokens from the Place if it has enough.
    OutputEdge
    An Edge meant to be linked from a Transition to a Place and add tokens to it.
    Place
    A base element which stores tokens.
    Transition
    A base element which can be triggered to make a step.
